    Aracni,a Rampage, Tankkor, and Paralysis enter the base. Aerostreak and 
Tarantulas greet them with cold eyes. They still hadnt gotten over her 
freaking out.
    "Quickstrike? Bugface, tell Quickstrike to meet me in my meeting room. We 
need to talk. Hurry up!" She demanded of Tarantulas.
    Tarantulas loomed over her. His transmetal body was much bigger then she 
was. "What ever you say, Commander." And left.
    Something about him wasnt right, Aracnia knew that he would betray her 
eventually.....but this was a bad time. "I had better keep an eye on him...."

    Tarantulas entered the brig where Quickstrike was tourturing Rat Trap. He 
looked over the small bot, who had gotten Aracnia pregnant. He wanted to bash 
his face in, but, good things come to those who wait.
    "The Commander wants you on the bridge, Commander Quickstrike. I suggest 
you leave the vermine to me."
